::Spears::

"Yeah, fine, peachy, just swell, couldn't be better. Now lets get to 
the pod."
She was trying to hide the fact that she wasn't just frantic on the 
flight, but panic striken.  She looked around for a moment. 
"That way right?" she said pointing.

> ::Ramulus::
> 
> Ramulus looks at Spears as she exits the pod. She had seemed almost 
frantic 
> on the flight.
> 
> "Are you allright?" he asks, "Other than sitting on your weapon, 
that is."
